
# 📖 Day 5 – ORDER BY, LIMIT & NULL

## Topics Covered

- ORDER BY
- LIMIT
- NULL

Ascending order

```sql
ORDER BY salary;
```

Descending order

```sql
ORDER BY salary DESC;
```

Top 5 rows

```sql
LIMIT 5;
```

Find NULL values

```sql
WHERE email IS NULL;
```

Find NOT NULL values

```sql
WHERE email IS NOT NULL;
```

